The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, ship, subway
 1. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 2. the pakistani is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the malaysian##7
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
10. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8
11. the german is not to the left of the baccarat-smoker##8
12. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
14. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
